snippet.title: The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing III - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Store page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/359900

Prepare for the final challenge - the last instalment of the Van Helsing trilogy is here! Van Helsing III is out NOW on Steam!

DevBlog: http://www.devblog.neocoregames.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/VanHelsingTheGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/VanHelsingGame

The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing III is a real-time Action RPG filled with fierce and demonic battles, memorable characters, and a refreshingly unique story loosely based on Bram Stoker's classic novel Dracula.
